description.narrative: This activity supports the sustainable development of the aquaculture sector in Timor-Leste through initiatives to increase availability of local fresh fish, access of fish to local markets, and fish consumption by Timorese. Support is delivered through the Partnership in Aquaculture Development in Timor-Leste (PADTL) Project.
